31
00:03:52,595 --> 00:03:54,998
Did you think it was a date?

32
00:03:55,065 --> 00:03:57,333
Honestly,
it never crossed my mind.

33
00:03:57,401 --> 00:03:59,770
Oh.

34
00:03:59,837 --> 00:04:01,705
Why not?

35
00:04:03,742 --> 00:04:05,877
You just don't seem
like you date.

36
00:04:05,944 --> 00:04:09,414
Oh. Too broken to date?

37
00:04:09,481 --> 00:04:11,449
You're not broken.

38
00:04:11,517 --> 00:04:13,920
- What's your excuse?
- For not dating?

39
00:04:13,987 --> 00:04:16,890
Why are you assuming
I don't date?

40
00:04:16,958 --> 00:04:18,858
Do you?

41
00:04:18,927 --> 00:04:20,460
No.

42
00:04:22,463 --> 00:04:24,731
Seems like something
for somebody else.

43
00:04:24,799 --> 00:04:27,435
I'm sure I'll become
that somebody someday,

44
00:04:27,502 --> 00:04:29,870
but right now I think too much.

45
00:04:29,939 --> 00:04:31,640
So,

46
00:04:31,707 --> 00:04:33,642
what are you gonna do?
Are you gonna try to think less,

47
00:04:33,709 --> 00:04:35,711
