62
00:05:26,136 --> 00:05:28,671
Who are you psychoanalyzing?

63
00:05:28,739 --> 00:05:31,574
My friend Tobias.

64
00:05:31,643 --> 00:05:36,381
I... Googled "psychopaths",

65
