you consider to be your flaws.

88
00:06:38,119 --> 00:06:41,622
Does that mean
that I'm a psychopath?

89
00:06:41,690 --> 00:06:43,925
You're not a psychopath,

90
00:06:43,993 --> 00:06:47,196
although you may be attracted
to them.

91
00:07:03,015 --> 00:07:05,583
The victim is Douglas Wilson,
a member

92
