an intellectual exercise.

101
00:07:36,887 --> 00:07:38,856
Well, in the narrow view
of forensics,

102
00:07:38,923 --> 00:07:41,724
- that's exactly what it is.
- They're not any easier, Jack.

103
00:07:44,796 --> 00:07:46,730
I shake it off,

104
00:07:46,798 --> 00:07:48,399
keep on looking.

105
00:07:48,467 --> 00:07:50,835
Good.

106
00:07:54,107 --> 00:07:57,108
You shake it off.
Get to work.

107
00:07:59,112 --> 00:08:02,149
We'll come back in
when you're ready for us.

108
00:09:08,593 --> 00:09:12,129
I open his throat
from the outside

109
00:09:12,196 --> 00:09:14,332
to open the trachea

110
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:16,433
and expose the vocal chords.

111
00:09:18,971 --> 00:09:21,406
I open his throat
