It's a serenade.

184
00:14:20,526 --> 00:14:25,497
No, this isn't how he kills. Normally,
he doesn't kill for an audience.

185
00:14:25,565 --> 00:14:28,684
And you believe he risked
getting caught for a serenade?

186
00:14:28,804 --> 00:14:30,804
I believe...

187
00:14:30,872 --> 00:14:33,974
he wants to show someone
how well he plays.

188
00:14:34,042 --> 00:14:37,278
<i>Do you remember</i>

189
00:14:37,346 --> 00:14:40,781
when I said Tobias was saying
very dark things?

190
00:14:40,850 --> 00:14:43,618
- I made note of it.
- Well, he said that he wanted

191
00:14:43,686 --> 00:14:48,024
