214
00:16:23,168 --> 00:16:27,104
- Was it an original composition?
- Something I've been writing.

215
00:16:27,172 --> 00:16:29,573
- You compose?
- I discover.

216
00:16:29,640 --> 00:16:32,110
Can't impose
traditional composition

217
00:16:32,178 --> 00:16:34,579
on an instrument
that's inherently free form.

218
00:16:34,646 --> 00:16:37,049
What instrument
would that be?

219
