222
00:16:44,292 --> 00:16:45,725
And so can a violin,

223
00:16:45,793 --> 00:16:48,561
or a trombone.

224
00:16:48,629 --> 00:16:52,266
It seems we are both comfortable
playing between conventional notes.

225
00:16:52,334 --> 00:16:54,803
I hear the symphony's

226
