looking for a new trombonist.

227
00:16:57,239 --> 00:16:59,608
Altogether horrible
what happened.

228
00:16:59,675 --> 00:17:01,276
Not altogether.

229
00:17:01,344 --> 00:17:03,779
It's an unfortunate way
to leave the symphony, yes,

230
00:17:03,847 --> 00:17:06,782
but I can't help thinking
the orchestra will be better

231
00:17:06,850 --> 00:17:09,653
-for it.
